---
title: Creamy Bacon & Mushroom Gnocchi with Parmesan Cheese
description: Have you tried pan-frying gnocchi? It becomes soft in the middle and a little bit crispy on the outside – in other words, totally irresistible! Give it a whirl and then smother it in this sumptuous bacon and mushroom cream sauce. Perfection!
